+ * enum adv7511_up_conversion - Selects the upscaling conversion method
+ * @ADV7511_UP_CONVERSION_ZERO_ORDER: Use zero order up conversion
+ * @ADV7511_UP_CONVERSION_FIRST_ORDER: Use first order up conversion
